<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_b61210dbac52.aspx"><b>郑风·扬之水</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contsonb61210dbac52">
<p>扬之水，不流束楚。终鲜兄弟，维予与女。无信人之言，人实诳女。<br />扬之水，不流束薪。终鲜兄弟，维予二人。无信人之言，人实不信。</p>
